snippet: Hands stuffed into his pockets on a chilly night, Aaron Rodgers warmed up near the space heaters on Green Bay's sideline. He smiled as he patted teammates on their helmets....

headline.print_headline: Rodgers Throws 6 TDs, Packers Rout Bears 55-14
headline.main: Rodgers Throws 6 TDs, Packers Rout Bears 55-14

lead_paragraph: Hands stuffed into his pockets on a chilly night, Aaron Rodgers warmed up near the space heaters on Green Bay's sideline. He smiled as he patted teammates on their helmets.
